.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the new true location of the npc
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/monster.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the true location of the npc.  This is
the real room it is in, not the room it is currently in.
